{"tid":620896,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7口罩男闖先達搗亂 手機店東疑遭報復圍毆","createTime":"2018-04-07T22:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T02:28:22.000Z","uid":18348,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8dbcd41d4d8b4c88abf5aa214b0fe323c669a6cc","tid":620896,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T22:13:40.000Z","msg":"旺角先達發生傷人刑毀案。據讀者提供的閉路電視片段，昨晚7時許，7名戴Cap帽口罩惡漢分別持鐵通及鐵鎚闖入地下一間手機店搗亂，擊毀一個飾櫃玻璃，並狂毆店內一名男店東，他走避不及面部受傷，惡漢逞兇後分批離去。商場內其他店舖職員報案，警員接報到場，將傷者送往廣華醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，該手機店於4月3日曾發生糾紛，據報一名男子與該店店員因買賣手機問題爭執，雙方一度大打出手，事後該名男顧客遭店東及多名店員㩒地制服，警方正調查兩案是否有關。<br />\n警方發言人指，昨晚約7時44分接獲一名39歲男子報案，指有7名男子手持鐵通等武器到其店舖搗亂，事件中他面部紅腫，警員到場時，兇徒已逃去，事主事後由警員送院，警方暫列傷人及刑事毀壞案，正追緝7名兇徒，並調查案件原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180408/58045915\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F58045915&d=Bh7YQzlcE7k%2FbGWz9OV7KgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=2981684d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F58045915&h=c6dab341\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180408/58045915</a>"},{"pid":"4292990077f9f4baf864bb627d184e76fb0a2fa6","tid":620896,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T22:22:33.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗.jpg"},{"pid":"225041a79ff48edac9a9140b48b6d75c406bd514","tid":620896,"uid":10079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T22:26:41.000Z","msg":"打狗棒法"},{"pid":"d1a96a3aba9bb607442aed4b6b71d3432702a3b9","tid":620896,"uid":17646,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T22:29:25.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦<br />\n制服人地，人地梗係唔服啦"},{"pid":"52048c389269a96b10c8c18c9daf182eeb1b18af","tid":620896,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T23:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" 